{"tid":1573646,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你見到手足打藍絲，仲會猶疑應唔應該打嘅...","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T05:35:37.000Z","uid":237194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"163fe1d446c24acd851398c09c7023c70c9956f3","tid":1573646,"uid":237194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"相信好多同我一樣咁和理非、大愛左膠、注重道德論述嘅巴絲，琴晚見到手足打藍絲打到人地瞓哂地，第一下都會猶疑，係咪重手左呢?甚或應唔應該做出超越自衛程度的還擊?<br />\n<br />\n但係今朝瞓醒一覺我諗清楚喇，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>一定支持手足還擊！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你仲有道德上嘅猶疑，覺得藍絲都係人，我地唔可以用不道德嘅方式對付對家嘅話<br />\n<br />\n咁我想講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>但係對家從來冇同我地講過道德!!</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警攞正牌打手足，黑社會、藍絲群出打人，黑警護航。當對家唔講道德，而我地仲被道德綁住嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>輸嘅一定係我地</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人已經被非暴力潔癖洗腦左太耐<br />\n沒有一場革命可以不暴力而成功<br />\n<br />\n眾多深入藍絲群組嘅手足已經講左，藍絲都係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>勝利球迷、欺善怕惡、見風駛舵</strong></span>，見到我地還拖，藍絲係會驚，覺得唔值為左幾百蚊俾人打，唔敢再出嚟亂打人<br />\n<br />\n民調亦已經顯示左，香港人對以武制暴接受程度係愈嚟愈高 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NeF5NL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NeF5NL.png&h=54e8a020&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(<a href=\"https://medium.com/@leungkaichihk/民意冇逆轉-10f90d0061a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40leungkaichihk%2F%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E5%86%87%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89-10f90d0061a9&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xbBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=f364dd6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@leungkaichihk/民意冇逆轉-10f90d0061a9</a>)<br />\n唔洗驚還拖會民意逆轉<img s